o more running ref.exe and fc\n- gen_cloud stays but isn't used in correctness testing\n\nThe user said \"просто вывести результат в консоль, ни на чём их не тестируя / не сравнивая\" — this is wrong. The mentor still wants testing via findstr, just without a separate reference program. The expected answers are \"проверенными глазами\" — known correct values that you hardcode in the test script and compare against.\n\nSo I should correct the user's understanding: they still need to test and compare — just with hardcoded known answers instead of a reference implementation.",
